task.summary: Added 3 commented work-in-progress methods. WARNINGS: a. I have not coordinated with mechanical engineers on the exact layout of hardware, so certain objects may be missing or declared under the wrong class | b. certain variables used in the methods are not defined and need to be replaced with real values.

Restructured the Avocado folder - hardware will now be stored in separate files under the Hardware folder. Also created an TeleOP, Autonomous folder and a Vision folder for work-in-progress/standalone vision files.
Changed the name of the OpMode
Imported needed libraries into Autonomous, added comments to Robot.java, fixed lift binary method.
Updated Robot.java to include Encoder Drive. Copied Constants.java from Aditya.
